eed. Even though generated tests might not require it, using TestKit would facilitate message handling. Without it, I could explore using the ask pattern, especially since pekko ask is related to scala futures and Java's CompletableFuture. I should check the relevant classes to clarify this.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_deek6y3Vu5QDMPzUhRpt8K3k|fc_0d60a974f43c7c7c016a42bf4b7f548193abd42b3557afc676", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "jar tf /home/vjovanov/.m2/repository/org/apache/pekko/pekko-actor_2.13/2.0.0-M1/pekko-actor_2.13-2.0.0-M1.jar | grep '^org/apache/pekko/pattern/' | head -60 && jar tf /home/vjovanov/.m2/repository/org/apache/pekko/pekko-actor_2.13/2.0.0-M1/pekko-actor_2.13-2.0.0-M1.jar | grep '^org/apache/pekko/testkit' | head"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3661, "output": 669, "cacheRead": 19968, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 24298, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1782759232516, "responseId": "resp_0d60a974f43c7c7c016a42bf4103a08193945697bd9f394390"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_deek6y3Vu5QDMPzUhRpt8K3k|fc_0d60a974f43c7c7c016a42bf4b7f548193abd42b3557afc676", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM warning: Insufficient space for shared memory file:\n   1313266\nTry using the -Djava.io.tmpdir= option to select an alternate temp location.\n\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AbstractCircuitBreaker.class\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AbstractPromiseActorRef.class\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AskPromiseRef$.class\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AskPromiseRef.class\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AskSupport.class\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AskTimeoutException.class\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AskableActorRef$.class\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AskableActorRef.class\norg/apache/pekko/pattern/AskableActorSelection$.c